title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jul 22 2021

description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2: Clay and Buck compare the reasoned, rational vaccine positions of Dr. Rand Paul and Governor Ron DeSantis with the raving lunacy of Joy Behar. Don Lemon argues for the Democrat position on eliminating the filibuster as moderator of town hall with Biden. Biden goes for guns. Don Lemon doesn't challenge Biden's nonsensical answer on asylum seekers from Cuba.
